  "text": "In order to address this issue, we investigate the use of hard constraints to enforce such global properties at the sampling phase on the generated sequence. Our goal is to express these properties as a Constraint Satisfaction Problem (CSP), and to sample solutions of the CSP with the probability given by the Markov model. Several results have been obtained toward this aim [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
